author: Brian Flood
title: CNN's April Ryan asks if protesters of stay-at-home guidelines should decline medical care if they get coronavirus
description: CNN political analyst April Ryan raised eyebrows on Monday by asking if people who protest stay-at-home mandates should be forced to decline medical attention if they test positive for coronavirus.
